 sermons, almost all that survives from his pen.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 7aRELIGION / Monasticism.2bisacsh1 aOCSO, M. Chrysogonus Waddell, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPerigo, Grace, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertGorgias Press Backlist eBook-Package 2001-2013z978311102414108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertGorgias Press Backlist eBook-Package 2001-2015z97831106630370 cprintz978160724202440uhttps://doi.org/10.31826/978146321832440uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781463218324423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781463218324/original  a978-3-11-066303-7  Gorgias Press Backlist eBook-Package 2001-2015c2001d2015  a978-3-11-102414-1  Gorgias Press Backlist eBook-Package 2001-2013c2001d2013  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK